    "h1": "Hydrolix",
    "h1_count": 1,
    "blockquote": "Hydrolix is a real-time data platform built for massive scale without compromises on data quality, query performance, retention, or cost. The platform combines stream processing, indexed search, decoupled storage, and industry-leading compression to deliver sub-second query performance on trillion-row datasets while dramatically reducing the cost of high-volume log data. Where traditional solutions force organizations to choose between cost and performance-sampling data, tiering storage, or discarding logs-Hydrolix eliminates those trade-offs, keeping all data hot and queryable whether it is a minute or a year old.",
